{
  "texts": [
    "It is possible that one of the AI functions did not add value on its own, but only benefited from the added value of the others.",
    "To account for this, only three AI functions were included in the experimental study from the outset.",
    "Conceptually, these three functions provided added value to the military analysis.",
    "An additional post-hoc survey was conducted to take this into account.",
    "However, these are subjective assessments of the participants and do not allow any causal conclusions to be drawn."
  ]
}